snippet.title: Pokémon Gold Version and Pokémon Silver Version - Launch Trailer (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
Return to the region of Johto in Pokémon Gold Version and Pokémon Silver version, out now on Nintendo eShop for Nintendo 3DS family systems.

#Pokemon #3DS #2DS #Nintendo
